改<br />\n<br />\n1.喺連登貼新聞貼返link 比人賺click rate廣告費 (只限非親共/黃營媒體)同埋盡量唔好講哂所有內容 鼓勵人click入去睇<br />\n<br />\n2.見到內容農場文唔好理 尢其fb好多文宣大台都係咁 仲好多時cap圖抄新聞就算 link都唔比<br />\n<br />\n3.未fact check既野保持距離 避免過於肯定 保持獨立思考 杜絕假新聞 不要過於相信陰謀論<br />\n<br />\n第1、2點例如 金水、香港地、巴打絲打facebook club呢啲最鍾意cap新聞圖就post上去 搞到蘋果立場冇哂錢賺<br />\n<br />\n［慶祝夠未］警 世 文！一齊打返起文宣戰線好嗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1890283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1890283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"328d3d9ad960f5a2d384c2d29dbfe08e52e823b9","tid":1892922,"uid":324229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T01:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fY1whTu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfY1whTu.png&h=8388b3d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b1e053570c1a702e9826eb3b8e6be99082ca316","tid":1892922,"uid":324229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T01:33:06.000Z","msg":"屯門聽日(2月23日)有活動 求推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1892049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1892049</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0eb0a6c91c81b266785b8b47b565ae7339fa4db3","tid":1892922,"uid":103438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b1e053570c1a702e9826eb3b8e6be99082ca316","tid":1892922,"uid":324229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T01:33:06.000Z","msg":"屯門聽日(2月23日)有活動 求推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1892049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1892049</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T01:34:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b79650eb17c2a2b6b93f6b483afac5a89633fa","tid":1892922,"uid":103438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b96cd632228f84e4dd2d44195ed2eb516829a591","tid":1892922,"uid":242771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit